{"type":"message","id":"6eb440e7","parentId":"817516c6","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:31:39.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了AuthService.cs的代码。让我分析一下异常信息泄露的问题：\n\n1. `RegisterAsync`方法中有两个异常抛出：\n   - \"用户名已存在\" - 这个相对安全，但不应该让攻击者枚举用户名\n   - \"邮箱已存在\" - 同样，不应该让攻击者枚举邮箱\n\n2. `LoginAsync`方法中有一个异常抛出：\n   - \"用户名或密码错误\" - 这个是安全的，没有泄露具体哪个错误\n\n主要问题是：\n1. 在注册时，错误信息过于具体，攻击者可以通过注册接口枚举已存在的用户名和邮箱\n2. 没有日志记录，无法追踪失败尝试\n3. 异常信息应该改为更通用的提示\n\n修复方案：\n1. 将注册时的具体错误改为通用的\"注册失败，请检查输入信息\"\n2. 添加日志记录（使用ILogger）\n3. 在日志中记录详细信息，但只返回通用提示给用户\n4. 考虑添加登录失败次数限制\n\n让我修改代码：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"【分析AuthService.cs异常信息泄露问题】\n\n发现以下安全隐患：\n\n1. **注册接口信息泄露**：\n   - \"用户名已存在\" - 攻击者可枚举用户名\n   - \"邮箱已存在\" - 攻击者可枚举邮箱\n\n2. **缺少日志记录**：无法追踪异常和失败尝试\n\n3. **异常信息过于详细**：应改为通用提示\n\n立即修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1ce0c41f09a148d08f3115e6","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Application/Services/AuthService.cs","old_string":"using Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration;\nusing System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt;\nusing System.Security.Claims;\nusing System.Text;\nusing BCrypt.Net;\nusing Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;\nusing Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Application.Services;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 认证服务\n/// </summary>\npublic class AuthService\n{\n    private readonly TianyouDbContext _context;\n    private readonly IConfiguration _configuration;\n    \n    public AuthService(TianyouDbContext context, IConfiguration configuration)\n    {\n        _context = context;\n        _configuration = configuration;\n    }","new_string":"using Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration;\nusing Microsoft.Extensions.Logging;\nusing System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt;\nusing System.Security.Claims;\nusing System.Text;\nusing BCrypt.Net;\nusing Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;\nusing Tianyou.Domain.Entities;\nusing Tianyou.Infrastructure.Data;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Application.Services;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 认证服务\n/// </summary>\npublic class AuthService\n{\n    private readonly TianyouDbContext _context;\n    private readonly IConfiguration _configuration;\n    private readonly ILogger<AuthService> _logger;\n\n    public AuthService(TianyouDbContext context, IConfiguration configuration, ILogger<AuthService> logger)\n    {\n        _context = context;\n        _configuration = configuration;\n        _logger = logger;\n    }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1047,"output":628,"cacheRead":14528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16203,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774416679514}}
