{"type":"message","id":"20dfd271","parentId":"86df4ddd","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:32:03.145Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我需要修改LoginAsync方法，添加日志记录。虽然\"用户名或密码错误\"已经是安全的，但我应该添加日志记录来追踪失败的登录尝试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dd03c71fc2be478da52e4358","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Application/Services/AuthService.cs","old_string":"    /// <summary>\n    /// 用户登录\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<(User user, string token)> LoginAsync(string username, string password)\n    {\n        var user = await _context.Users\n            .Include(u => u.Roles)\n            .ThenInclude(r => r.Permissions)\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(u => u.Username == username);\n        \n        if (user == null || !BCrypt.Net.BCrypt.Verify(password, user.PasswordHash))\n        {\n            throw new Exception(\"用户名或密码错误\");\n        }","new_string":"    /// <summary>\n    /// 用户登录\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<(User user, string token)> LoginAsync(string username, string password)\n    {\n        var user = await _context.Users\n            .Include(u => u.Roles)\n            .ThenInclude(r => r.Permissions)\n            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(u => u.Username == username);\n\n        if (user == null || !BCrypt.Net.BCrypt.Verify(password, user.PasswordHash))\n        {\n            _logger.LogWarning(\"登录失败：用户名或密码错误 - Username: {Username}, IP: 需要从上下文获取\", username);\n            throw new Exception(\"用户名或密码错误\");\n        }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":478,"output":334,"cacheRead":16192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774416712190}}
